00:14:35,380 --> 00:14:36,060
Young lady,

284
00:14:36,180 --> 00:14:37,220
snake is homophonic

285
00:14:37,220 --> 00:14:38,700
to lady in dialect.

286
00:14:39,140 --> 00:14:40,700
But the parrot only said this word

287
00:14:40,700 --> 00:14:41,700
in dialect,

288
00:14:41,700 --> 00:14:43,180
and the other words in official language.

289
00:14:43,220 --> 00:14:44,820
The snake charmer must have done it on purpose.

290
00:14:45,300 --> 00:14:46,380
In theatres, a joke is going around

291
00:14:46,380 --> 00:14:47,780
about the Deputy Censor.

292
00:14:47,780 --> 00:14:48,820
When he was the principal graduate,

293
00:14:49,340 --> 00:14:51,300
he married the elder sister and the younger sister,

294
00:14:51,580 --> 00:14:53,220
to flatter their influential father.

295
00:14:53,300 --> 00:14:55,220
That’s the younger going after the elder.

296
00:15:03,860 --> 00:15:05,500
The ex-owner of Winehouse Fan passed away.

297
00:15:06,060 --> 00:15:07,540
His son failed in doing business.

298
00:15:08,460 --> 00:15:09,700
With years of losses,

299
00:15:09,780 --> 00:15:10,980
he could no longer run it.

300
00:15:12,900 --> 00:15:14,460
He wants to shut it down

301
00:15:14,620 --> 00:15:17,660
and auction all the assets and lands for debts.

302
00:15:19,500 --> 00:15:20,540
Winehouse Fan?

303
00:15:22,100 --> 00:15:23,580
Isn’t this the best in the Capital?

304
00:15:26,180 --> 00:15:27,980
Even the envoy of Liao mentioned that

305
00:15:28,140 --> 00:15:30,420
he’d go to Winehouse Fan to have a few drinks,

306
00:15:30,700 --> 00:15:32,660
listen to the stories, enjoy dancing,

307
00:15:33,860 --> 00:15:35,060
and try all those delicacies

308
00:15:35,060 --> 00:15:36,020
after the annual court meeting.

309
00:15:36,860 --> 00:15:37,940
Exactly.

310
00:15:38,700 --> 00:15:40,300
= Han Qi, courtesy name Zhigui =
That’s why I bring up this

311
00:15:40,300 --> 00:15:41,180
as a government affair

312
00:15:41,500 --> 00:15:43,180
to ask you for advice, Your Majesty.

313
00:15:45,140 --> 00:15:45,940
Moreover,

314
00:15:46,540 --> 00:15:47,740
the new owner of Winehouse Fan

315
00:15:47,860 --> 00:15:50,340
is going to sell it to a rich merchant

316
00:15:51,300 --> 00:15:54,140
introduced by the manager.

317
00:15:54,860 --> 00:15:56,100
It’s hard to tell

318
00:15:56,540 --> 00:15:58,500
whether there’s any trade under the table.

319
00:15:58,580 --> 00:15:59,540
= Jia Changchao, courtesy name Ziming =

320
00:15:59,540 --> 00:16:00,340
Minister Han,

321
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:02,060
without any proof,

322
00:16:02,540 --> 00:16:04,060
you shouldn’t have slandered someone

323
00:16:04,260 --> 00:16:06,340
in front of His Majesty.

324
00:16:07,580 --> 00:16:08,780
The manager threatened the new owner that

325
00:16:08,940 --> 00:16:11,460
he’d be imprisoned and tortured

326
00:16:11,660 --> 00:16:13,660
if the due debt can’t be paid on time

327
00:16:14,220 --> 00:16:16,220
and inveigled him to sell Winehouse Fan

328
00:16:16,300 --> 00:16:18,020
to pay off the wine tax requested by the court.

329
00:16:18,820 --> 00:16:20,700
Then, the manager introduced the merchant, Chen

330
00:16:20,700 --> 00:16:22,300
to buy the lands

331
00:16:22,540 --> 00:16:24,260
with a price lower than the market value.

332
00:16:25,140 --> 00:16:27,220
I’m not making this up.

333
00:16:27,580 --> 00:16:28,860
I have authentic proofs for everything.

334
00:16:29,780 --> 00:16:30,540
Unless...

335
00:16:32,260 --> 00:16:33,220
Minister Jia knows some details about

336
00:16:33,540 --> 00:16:36,100
the sale of Winehouse Fan

337
00:16:36,940 --> 00:16:38,540
or some officials who are involved in.

338
00:16:39,660 --> 00:16:41,340
Substantial evidence will be needed

339
00:16:41,940 --> 00:16:43,380
for the discussion in front of His Majesty.

340
00:16:43,980 --> 00:16:44,740
What?

341
00:16:44,980 --> 00:16:45,940
What details?

342
00:16:46,340 --> 00:16:46,940
How...

343
00:16:47,420 --> 00:16:48,140
How come I...

344
00:16:48,460 --> 00:16:49,740
How come I know about this?

345
00:16:51,420 --> 00:16:52,220
Your Ma...

346
00:16:54,980 --> 00:16:56,700
I thought about it.

347
00:16:57,540 --> 00:16:59,660
Winehouse Fan has paid wine taxes for years

348
00:17:00,180 --> 00:17:02,100
and added luster to the Capital.

349
00:17:02,580 --> 00:17:03,500
Now it’s in trouble.

350
00:17:03,940 --> 00:17:05,820
We can somehow help.

351
00:17:06,780 --> 00:17:08,180
The ex-owner died abruptly.

352
00:17:08,540 --> 00:17:09,700
It’s an unexpected

353
00:17:09,780 --> 00:17:11,300
and irresistible disaster.

354
00:17:12,260 --> 00:17:13,100
Conventionally,

355
00:17:13,540 --> 00:17:14,660
tax in arrears

356
00:17:15,740 --> 00:17:16,740
can be postponed for six months

357
00:17:17,100 --> 00:17:18,540
and paid by month.

358
00:17:19,780 --> 00:17:20,980
As for the business,

359
00:17:26,940 --> 00:17:28,580
I’ll ask the ministries to give an order that

360
00:17:28,940 --> 00:17:30,260
three thousand inns

361
00:17:30,500 --> 00:17:32,820
shall buy wines from Winehouse Fan next year.

362
00:17:34,860 --> 00:17:35,900
It’s wise of you, Your Majesty.

363
00:17:41,980 --> 00:17:42,780
Yuansheng,

364
00:17:43,380 --> 00:17:45,700
I prayed every day

365
00:17:45,940 --> 00:17:47,820
that you could return home safely.

366
00:17:49,780 --> 00:17:51,260
I can’t pay what you’ve done for me

367
00:17:51,620 --> 00:17:53,020
all my life.

368
00:17:53,660 --> 00:17:54,780
= Landlady of Restaurant of Breeze, Zhang Lihua =
What are you talking about?

369
00:17:54,940 --> 00:17:56,020
You don’t need to pay anything.

370
00:17:56,940 --> 00:17:58,900
I’ve been widowed over these years

371
00:17:58,940 --> 00:18:00,060
and my son died at a young age.

372
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:01,300
I can count on no one,

373
00:18:01,980 --> 00:18:03,100
but you.

374
00:18:04,260 --> 00:18:06,340
= Restaurant of Breeze =
I always trust you the most.

375
00:18:06,340 --> 00:18:07,700
I’ll even have you

376
00:18:07,780 --> 00:18:09,500
run the restaurant in the future.

377
00:18:09,820 --> 00:18:10,500
Come.

378
00:18:23,260 --> 00:18:24,380
Several months ago,

379
00:18:25,020 --> 00:18:27,980
Chief Military Commissioner Zheng Jian

380
00:18:28,060 --> 00:18:31,700
accused Teng Zongliang,
Scholar of the Hall of Articles,

381
00:18:32,140 --> 00:18:34,260
= Fan Zhongyan, courtesy name Xiwen =
and Governor of Qing County,

382
00:18:34,460 --> 00:18:37,780
of abusing the government funds
when he was in charge of Jingzhou.

383
00:18:38,100 --> 00:18:39,860
Your Majesty sent

384
00:18:39,980 --> 00:18:41,740
the Investigating Censor to investigate it.

385
00:18:42,420 --> 00:18:45,380
Here’s
what Investigating Censor Liang Jian reported.

386
00:18:46,140 --> 00:18:46,980
Teng Zongliang

387
00:18:47,140 --> 00:18:49,620
used 160,000 strings of copper of government funds,

388
00:18:49,780 --> 00:18:51,780
some of which wasn’t recorded.

389
00:18:52,580 --> 00:18:54,740
He must have embezzled it.

390
00:19:00,260 --> 00:19:02,100
I believe in Teng Zongliang.

391
00:19:03,380 --> 00:19:05,540
Even if this is not defamation,

392
00:19:05,980 --> 00:19:07,260
it may not be the truth.

393
00:19:08,500 --> 00:19:10,340
Mr. Fan, do you have any evidence

394
00:19:10,740 --> 00:19:13,820
to turn down Censor Liang’s impeachment?

395
00:19:14,540 --> 00:19:16,220
I just heard that from you.

396
00:19:16,460 --> 00:19:18,100
How could I have any evidence?

397
00:19:18,900 --> 00:19:20,260
You just heard of it.

398
00:19:20,860 --> 00:19:22,620
But without investigation,

399
00:19:22,860 --> 00:19:24,940
you said it was defamation or not the truth.

400
00:19:25,580 --> 00:19:26,420
Mr. Fan,

401
00:19:26,860 --> 00:19:29,020
are you still fair?

402
00:19:30,740 --> 00:19:31,980
I never pretend

403
00:19:31,980 --> 00:19:32,940
to be fair.

404
00:19:33,660 --> 00:19:34,980
I do fair things.

405
00:19:36,060 --> 00:19:37,980
Teng and I took the imperial exam in the same year.

406
00:19:37,980 --> 00:19:39,020
We’re good friends.

407
00:19:39,500 --> 00:19:41,260
All these years,

408
00:19:41,260 --> 00:19:42,220
I know clearly how he works.

409
00:19:42,780 --> 00:19:44,700
And I know more clearly

410
00:19:44,740 --> 00:19:45,740
how many properties he has.

411
00:19:46,460 --> 00:19:48,820
If you accuse him of making mistakes in working,

412
00:19:49,060 --> 00:19:50,220
I won’t object right away.

413
00:19:50,540 --> 00:19:51,420
But if you accuse him of corruption,

414
00:19:52,100 --> 00:19:53,500
surely, I make a quick retort.

415
00:19:54,980 --> 00:19:56,540
That’s my loyalty to His Majesty.

416
00:19:57,860 --> 00:19:59,660
What Mr. Fan said

417
00:19:59,860 --> 00:20:01,340
makes a good point.

418
00:20:02,300 --> 00:20:04,700
But there’s evidence for

419
00:20:05,020 --> 00:20:07,220
what the Censor has reported.

420
00:20:07,780 --> 00:20:08,820
Mr. Fan,

421
00:20:09,580 --> 00:20:12,780
you use your friendship to prove what you said.

422
00:20:13,700 --> 00:20:15,540
Well, when you

423
00:20:16,100 --> 00:20:19,580
examine performances of officials,

424
00:20:19,700 --> 00:20:22,460
can we make some accused officials

425
00:20:22,820 --> 00:20:26,460
get away from the punishment

426
00:20:26,900 --> 00:20:28,260
by saying we’re good friends?

427
00:20:29,100 --> 00:20:29,980
Or...

428
00:20:30,660 --> 00:20:32,820
when you vouch for someone,

429
00:20:33,300 --> 00:20:36,020
he’ll be more credible?

430
00:20:40,540 --> 00:20:41,340
Draft the edict.

431
00:20:42,420 --> 00:20:44,540
Yan Du, Chamberlain of Ceremonies,
shall go to Binzhou

432
00:20:44,700 --> 00:20:46,020
and try the case

433
00:20:46,020 --> 00:20:47,740
of Teng Zongliang’s embezzlement

434
00:20:48,180 --> 00:20:49,300
and corruption.

435
00:20:50,340 --> 00:20:51,140
Ask Teng Zongliang

436
00:20:51,540 --> 00:20:53,580
to hand over all the government affairs

437
00:20:53,980 --> 00:20:55,100
and go to Binzhou for investigation.

438
00:20:58,100 --> 00:20:58,820
Your Majesty.

439
00:20:59,180 --> 00:21:00,500
Teng Zongliang is a capable man.

440
00:21:01,180 --> 00:21:02,420
Under his governing for years,

441
00:21:02,420 --> 00:21:03,700
people all live a peaceful life.

442
00:21:04,060 --> 00:21:06,900
Now we accuse an important official at border

443
00:21:07,260 --> 00:21:08,620
and suspend him for investigation

444
00:21:08,620 --> 00:21:10,580
after we’ve just made peace with enemies.

445
00:21:11,420 --> 00:21:12,820
I’m afraid that soldiers
and local people will feel uneasy.

446
00:21:14,340 --> 00:21:15,140
Fan Zhongyan.

447
00:21:16,260 --> 00:21:18,140
What do you rely on

448
00:21:18,460 --> 00:21:19,740
when you investigate officials’ performances,

449
00:21:20,060 --> 00:21:21,380
solid evidence

450
00:21:21,380 --> 00:21:22,220
or guarantee from his friends?

451
00:21:23,140 --> 00:21:24,380
If there’s controversial evidence,

452
00:21:24,380 --> 00:21:25,500
will you figure it out

453
00:21:25,860 --> 00:21:27,140
or let him go

454
00:21:27,140 --> 00:21:28,180
because of his capacity?

455
00:21:37,980 --> 00:21:38,780
I’m tired.

456
00:21:40,260 --> 00:21:41,300
So much for today.

457
00:21:42,460 --> 00:21:43,260
Draft the decree right now.

458
00:21:43,980 --> 00:21:44,940
Before tonight,

459
00:21:45,580 --> 00:21:47,740
Yan Du must leave the Capital for Binzhou.

460
00:22:07,420 --> 00:22:08,860
It hasn’t been a month since Madam Zhang gave birth

461
00:22:09,380 --> 00:22:10,220
and she’s sick.

462
00:22:11,100 --> 00:22:11,860
We’re so busy that

463
00:22:11,860 --> 00:22:13,060
we even need more maids.

464
00:22:13,900 --> 00:22:15,420
Why must you ask me to come here?

465
00:22:16,620 --> 00:22:18,900
Does she really lack maids?

466
00:22:19,180 --> 00:22:20,380
If she does,

467
00:22:20,780 --> 00:22:22,140
tell His Majesty

468
00:22:22,220 --> 00:22:24,020
and there will be new maids soon.

469
00:22:25,780 --> 00:22:27,260
You know

470
00:22:28,100 --> 00:22:29,700
Madam Zhang is only relieved

471
00:22:29,700 --> 00:22:31,100
when the baby is with me.

472
00:22:31,100 --> 00:22:32,900
= Yang Huaimin =

473
00:22:32,900 --> 00:22:34,620
She doesn’t have a son.

474
00:22:34,620 --> 00:22:35,860
Why is she afraid of being framed?

475
00:22:37,420 --> 00:22:40,020
Who will risk for a mere princess?

476
00:22:40,100 --> 00:22:41,620
She’s thinking too much.

477
00:22:43,420 --> 00:22:44,540
What do you want me for?

478
00:22:44,940 --> 00:22:46,140
If you want nothing, I’ll leave.

479
00:22:49,860 --> 00:22:51,580
She’s screwed.

480
00:22:55,860 --> 00:22:56,700
What do you mean?

481
00:22:57,660 --> 00:22:58,460
Screwed?

482
00:23:01,780 --> 00:23:03,460
Yesterday, physicians checked on Madam Zhang.

483
00:23:03,980 --> 00:23:05,340
I spent a lot of money,

484
00:23:05,340 --> 00:23:07,380
asking the head for some information.

485
00:23:08,020 --> 00:23:09,100
Even if she gets better,

486
00:23:09,500 --> 00:23:11,780
she can’t completely recover.

487
00:23:11,780 --> 00:23:12,820
She can hardly have another baby.

488
00:23:13,020 --> 00:23:14,940
And within six months or a year,

489
00:23:16,220 --> 00:23:17,820
she can’t sleep with His Majesty.

490
00:23:19,900 --> 00:23:23,500
Or she might be dead.

491
00:23:30,300 --> 00:23:31,380
You know what?

492
00:23:32,500 --> 00:23:34,460
We must have a plan.

493
00:23:36,380 --> 00:23:37,340
Plan?

494
00:23:39,500 --> 00:23:40,460
Don’t think I don’t know

495
00:23:40,500 --> 00:23:41,700
what you really want.

496
00:23:44,140 --> 00:23:44,940
I want to

497
00:23:44,940 --> 00:23:46,860
enjoy the wealth all my life.

498
00:23:47,940 --> 00:23:49,060
Do you want to

499
00:23:49,060 --> 00:23:50,260
serve the country and love the people?

500
00:23:50,900 --> 00:23:52,740
You used to smuggle things

501
00:23:52,740 --> 00:23:53,980
and sell girls.

502
00:23:53,980 --> 00:23:55,940
In the palace, you’re arrogant and domineering

503
00:23:56,100 --> 00:23:58,140
because His Majesty loves Madam Zhang.

504
00:23:58,140 --> 00:23:58,900
If she is not favored by His Majesty any more,

505
00:23:58,900 --> 00:24:00,820
you’ll suffer before me.

506
00:24:00,900 --> 00:24:01,900
So what?

507
00:24:03,100 --> 00:24:04,580
At the worst, I’ll just kill myself

508
00:24:04,580 --> 00:24:05,420
and end everything.

509
00:24:05,500 --> 00:24:06,580
Will I be afraid of you?

510
00:24:14,180 --> 00:24:16,700
You won’t be afraid of me.

511
00:24:18,340 --> 00:24:21,220
I just want you to care for yourself

512
00:24:22,180 --> 00:24:25,220
and consider for Chief Xia.

513
00:24:25,460 --> 00:24:26,500
Do you think

514
00:24:26,500 --> 00:24:27,820
it’s that easy to find

515
00:24:27,820 --> 00:24:28,900
a new master?

516
00:24:28,980 --> 00:24:29,980
You know what?

517
00:24:30,380 --> 00:24:31,660
Over so many years,

518
00:24:31,660 --> 00:24:32,700
Madam Zhang is the only woman

519
00:24:32,700 --> 00:24:34,540
that His Majesty loves the most.

520
00:24:34,620 --> 00:24:35,820
I didn’t ask you to

521
00:24:35,820 --> 00:24:37,060
find another master.

522
00:24:37,060 --> 00:24:38,260
I mean you should find someone

523
00:24:38,260 --> 00:24:40,300
to serve His Majesty for Madam Zhang.

524
00:24:42,380 --> 00:24:44,100
When Empress Dowager Zhangxian was alive,

525
00:24:44,100 --> 00:24:44,980
Empress Dowager Zhangyi

526
00:24:44,980 --> 00:24:46,060
gave birth to His Majesty

527
00:24:46,100 --> 00:24:48,340
and Empress Dowager Zhanghui
served the late Emperor.

528
00:24:48,780 --> 00:24:49,780
Even now,

529
00:24:50,260 --> 00:24:52,820
Madam Miao joins hands

530
00:24:52,820 --> 00:24:54,180
with the Empress.

531
00:25:01,500 --> 00:25:03,060
I need some time to find a maid.

532
00:25:04,900 --> 00:25:05,900
The maid

533
00:25:06,980 --> 00:25:08,900
should be beautiful enough

534
00:25:09,220 --> 00:25:10,500
and approved by Madam Zhang.

535
00:25:10,780 --> 00:25:12,540
In the Pavilion of Luan,

536
00:25:12,540 --> 00:25:14,340
who is beautiful enough to satisfy His Majesty?

537
00:25:16,100 --> 00:25:18,100
Madam Zhang is too jealous.

538
00:25:19,060 --> 00:25:20,740
When His Majesty looked at someone

539
00:25:20,740 --> 00:25:22,020
or teased someone,

540
00:25:22,020 --> 00:25:23,860
she kicked them out.

541
00:25:24,100 --> 00:25:25,420
Only ugly and stupid maids

542
00:25:25,420 --> 00:25:27,060
can stay.

543
00:25:28,140 --> 00:25:29,300
My dear sister.

544
00:25:29,300 --> 00:25:31,860
She isn’t available for at least six months.

545
00:25:32,100 --> 00:25:33,460
However much His Majesty loves her,

546
00:25:33,700 --> 00:25:34,900
when no one can take care of him

547
00:25:34,900 --> 00:25:36,340
or warm the bed for him,

548
00:25:36,340 --> 00:25:37,820
would he still come every day

549
00:25:37,820 --> 00:25:39,380
to serve her instead?

550
00:26:05,380 --> 00:26:06,340
Why don’t you sit down?

551
00:26:06,580 --> 00:26:07,580
It’s inconvenient to talk.

552
00:26:12,100 --> 00:26:13,500
You helped quite a lot

553
00:26:13,780 --> 00:26:15,020
when solving Huang Dehe’s case

554
00:26:15,100 --> 00:26:16,460
and you instigated rebellion
within civilians in Xixia

555
00:26:16,700 --> 00:26:18,060
when we made peace with Xixia.

556
00:26:18,900 --> 00:26:20,460
You made contributions twice.

557
00:26:20,500 --> 00:26:22,020
If you had accepted the awards,

558
00:26:22,180 --> 00:26:23,940
you would have been an official long ago.

559
00:26:29,060 --> 00:26:29,900
I come here

560
00:26:30,100 --> 00:26:31,620
for Winehouse Fan.

561
00:26:32,780 --> 00:26:34,140
His Majesty told the ministries that

562
00:26:34,340 --> 00:26:35,820
if someone could pay

563
00:26:35,820 --> 00:26:37,460
the taxes Winehouse Fan owed last year

564
00:26:37,700 --> 00:26:39,380
and taxes for 25,000 kilos of wine next year,

565
00:26:39,860 --> 00:26:40,820
the outstanding taxes

566
00:26:41,060 --> 00:26:42,580
of Winehouse Fan

567
00:26:42,660 --> 00:26:43,540
can be postponed for six months

568
00:26:43,900 --> 00:26:45,220
and paid by month.

569
00:26:45,980 --> 00:26:48,660
Three thousand inns shall buy wine
from Winehouse Fan.

570
00:26:51,140 --> 00:26:53,220
My foster mother just told me about it yesterday.

571
00:26:53,620 --> 00:26:55,060
Winehouse Fan did good business.

572
00:26:55,900 --> 00:26:58,020
But it went broke,

573
00:26:58,060 --> 00:26:59,060
because someone did something to it.

574
00:27:01,460 --> 00:27:02,900
Last year,

575
00:27:03,380 --> 00:27:04,980
some leading singing and dancing girls

576
00:27:05,260 --> 00:27:06,900
suddenly quitted their jobs.

577
00:27:07,580 --> 00:27:09,620
Then the chef got a new job.

578
00:27:10,580 --> 00:27:11,780
And then,

579
00:27:12,180 --> 00:27:14,860
5,000 kilos of wine became mildewed in the rain.

580
00:27:15,380 --> 00:27:17,100
The shopkeeper was ignorant.

581
00:27:17,700 --> 00:27:18,620
But the manager

582
00:27:18,620 --> 00:27:19,980
has worked there for twenty years.

583
00:27:20,380 --> 00:27:21,700
How could so many things

584
00:27:21,700 --> 00:27:23,100
happen in merely one year?

585
00:27:26,900 --> 00:27:27,980
Last year,

586
00:27:28,180 --> 00:27:29,620
manager of Winehouse Fan became relatives

587
00:27:29,740 --> 00:27:31,380
with the butler of Mr. Jia Changchao

588
00:27:31,380 --> 00:27:32,340
by marriage.

589
00:27:32,780 --> 00:27:34,180
Mr. Chen, the merchant,

590
00:27:34,380 --> 00:27:35,780
did wood business

591
00:27:35,940 --> 00:27:37,700
with some cousins of

592
00:27:37,780 --> 00:27:39,060
Mr. Xia Song.

593
00:27:40,620 --> 00:27:43,140
That’s all we can tell.

594
00:27:43,860 --> 00:27:45,020
Mr. Han,

595
00:27:45,700 --> 00:27:46,980
hope you can understand.

596
00:27:48,620 --> 00:27:49,420
I see.

597
00:27:51,180 --> 00:27:52,700
That’s why

598
00:27:52,860 --> 00:27:54,140
I discussed about it

599
00:27:54,140 --> 00:27:55,020
in front of His Majesty.

600
00:27:56,740 --> 00:27:57,900
Now, three thousand inns

601
00:27:58,060 --> 00:27:59,460
will buy wine from Winehouse Fan.

602
00:28:00,300 --> 00:28:02,020
Guaranteeing the sales of wine next year

603
00:28:02,020 --> 00:28:02,940
isn’t the most important thing.

604
00:28:03,500 --> 00:28:04,340
The key point is

605
00:28:05,060 --> 00:28:08,060
that the imperial court shows its attitude.

606
00:28:13,180 --> 00:28:14,260
Mr. Han, you’re right.

607
00:28:17,140 --> 00:28:18,500
My foster mother

608
00:28:18,860 --> 00:28:20,540
and Ms. He with the Bian River Dockyard

609
00:28:20,540 --> 00:28:21,700
will be my guarantor.

610
00:28:22,860 --> 00:28:25,020
But as for the auction fee...

611
00:28:25,620 --> 00:28:27,380
I have the two rewards from the imperil court.

612
00:28:28,180 --> 00:28:29,260
And I’ve sold

613
00:28:29,980 --> 00:28:31,380
all the properties

614
00:28:31,620 --> 00:28:33,540
gained from the lawsuit against my aunt.

615
00:28:33,780 --> 00:28:36,620
I still lack half of the minimum amount.

616
00:28:37,500 --> 00:28:39,500
I can’t guarantee you now.

617
00:28:40,420 --> 00:28:42,620
But if I can raise the money in ten days,

618
00:28:43,500 --> 00:28:44,420
I will strive for that.

619
00:28:47,660 --> 00:28:50,900
= Fan Mansion =

620
00:28:51,860 --> 00:28:52,820
Don’t bother to tell Xiwen.

621
00:28:53,060 --> 00:28:54,500
Just take us to him.

622
00:28:54,500 --> 00:28:55,140
Okay.

623
00:29:04,260 --> 00:29:05,020
Mr. Fan.

624
00:29:14,500 --> 00:29:15,260
Stand up.

625
00:29:16,060 --> 00:29:17,340
I just come to have a look

626
00:29:17,340 --> 00:29:18,180
on the spur of the moment.

627
00:29:23,340 --> 00:29:25,220
What a shabby house

628
00:29:25,500 --> 00:29:26,820
for an assistant administrator.

629
00:29:28,060 --> 00:29:30,420
I haven’t bought a house in the Capital.

630
00:29:30,700 --> 00:29:32,140
I rent this house.

631
00:29:32,940 --> 00:29:34,780
My wife or children haven’t come with me.

632
00:29:38,460 --> 00:29:40,140
Go boil some water.

633
00:29:40,420 --> 00:29:41,500
Don’t make tea.

634
00:29:41,860 --> 00:29:43,220
The chair is kind of broken.

635
00:29:43,420 --> 00:29:44,540
I’ll go find you a cushion.

636
00:29:44,540 --> 00:29:45,260
It’s okay.

637
00:29:46,300 --> 00:29:48,700
You can sit on it. Why can’t I?

638
00:29:54,660 --> 00:29:57,660
Xiwen, I know you’re poor.

639
00:29:58,660 --> 00:30:00,340
I bring some dishes.

640
00:30:00,980 --> 00:30:03,420
But I didn’t know you are so poor that

641
00:30:04,100 --> 00:30:06,700
= I, Fan Zhongyan, =
you only had books, a table and chairs.

642
00:30:07,700 --> 00:30:10,260
Clothes and books are put on the ground.

643
00:30:10,980 --> 00:30:12,940
Your Majesty, I’m going to check

644
00:30:13,540 --> 00:30:14,540
if the Ministry of Revenue

645
00:30:14,540 --> 00:30:17,100
has default on Mr. Fan’s salary.

646
00:30:21,580 --> 00:30:22,860
You’re ready

647
00:30:23,660 --> 00:30:26,260
to get packed and leave the Capital at any time.

648
00:30:30,660 --> 00:30:32,300
To fulfill my job this time,

649
00:30:32,500 --> 00:30:34,660
I must have nothing to worry about.

650
00:30:35,620 --> 00:30:37,260
Why must I keep worldly possessions

651
00:30:37,580 --> 00:30:39,580
to make trouble?

652
00:30:45,700 --> 00:30:47,180
Worldly possessions to make trouble?

653
00:30:47,300 --> 00:30:48,260
Good point.

654
00:30:49,740 --> 00:30:50,620
But...

655
00:30:51,900 --> 00:30:53,940
Mr. Yan, most officials

656
00:30:54,420 --> 00:30:55,940
and even I

657
00:30:56,780 --> 00:30:58,420
have got many worldly possessions.

658
00:31:00,980 --> 00:31:02,580
You don’t want such things.

659
00:31:03,500 --> 00:31:04,660
No wonder you don’t understand

660
00:31:04,860 --> 00:31:07,340
common people who love them.

661
00:31:09,220 --> 00:31:11,500
It’s been seven months since the reform.

662
00:31:12,180 --> 00:31:14,380
More than 20% of officials have been fired.

663
00:31:15,980 --> 00:31:16,860
The most incompetent officials

664
00:31:16,860 --> 00:31:18,140
have mostly been fired.

665
00:31:18,140 --> 00:31:21,660
Why don’t we lay it aside?

666
00:31:21,980 --> 00:31:23,260
The spring exam is coming.

667
00:31:23,260 --> 00:31:25,100
We’ve made peace with Xixia.

668
00:31:25,460 --> 00:31:28,580
The border is still worrying.

669
00:31:28,580 --> 00:31:29,700
What’s the conflict

670
00:31:30,300 --> 00:31:31,940
with dismissing officials?

671
00:31:32,180 --> 00:31:33,220
With incorruptible officials, for other things

672
00:31:33,380 --> 00:31:35,020
we can have twice the result with half the effort.

673
00:31:36,380 --> 00:31:38,420
There is always an order of priority.

674
00:31:38,820 --> 00:31:42,020
The situation of redundant officials is improved.

675
00:31:43,100 --> 00:31:44,700
But there are many censures.

676
00:31:44,900 --> 00:31:47,580
Why don’t we slow it down to see the effect?

677
00:31:48,700 --> 00:31:50,140
The redundancy is a chronic disease.

678
00:31:50,260 --> 00:31:51,660
It has worsened in the past decades.

679
00:31:52,180 --> 00:31:53,980
Therefore, His Majesty, you,

680
00:31:53,980 --> 00:31:55,060
and other officials

681
00:31:55,060 --> 00:31:56,540
think we must solve the problem.

682
00:31:57,020 --> 00:31:58,180
You then make up your mind

683
00:31:58,420 --> 00:32:00,700
and use me to take harsh measures.

684
00:32:01,780 --> 00:32:03,180
Things are getting better.

685
00:32:03,500 --> 00:32:04,900
But because of the censures,

686
00:32:05,580 --> 00:32:07,420
will His Majesty and officials

687
00:32:07,500 --> 00:32:08,500
get back various concerns

688
00:32:08,660 --> 00:32:10,660
about the harm from harsh measures

689
00:32:11,180 --> 00:32:12,140
that they used to have

690
00:32:13,300 --> 00:32:14,660
and give up halfway?

691
00:32:14,860 --> 00:32:16,900
In either curing a disease or governing a nation,

692
00:32:17,180 --> 00:32:19,300
we can’t completely eradicated evils.

693
00:32:19,780 --> 00:32:22,420
There might be accidental injury.

694
00:32:22,700 --> 00:32:23,820
For the fear of accidental injury,

695
00:32:23,900 --> 00:32:25,260
we’re going to keep some evils

696
00:32:25,260 --> 00:32:26,660
or stop completely solving the problem?

697
00:32:34,060 --> 00:32:35,100
Does this problem happen

698
00:32:36,340 --> 00:32:37,820
only because of falling standards

699
00:32:38,380 --> 00:32:40,060
over the decades?

700
00:32:40,900 --> 00:32:44,020
What’s the root cause?

701
00:32:49,780 --> 00:32:52,500
When I came to the Capital before the new year,

702
00:32:52,860 --> 00:32:54,220
I visited Prime Minister Lv.

703
00:32:54,780 --> 00:32:56,620
He told me

704
00:32:57,980 --> 00:32:58,900
he was afraid that

705
00:32:59,340 --> 00:33:00,300
the root cause was from

706
00:33:00,300 --> 00:33:01,660
the ancestral rules.

707
00:33:03,180 --> 00:33:05,060
But I believe

708
00:33:06,140 --> 00:33:07,860
that’s only Prime Minister Lv’s opinion.

709
00:33:10,300 --> 00:33:11,020
Be specific.

710
00:33:12,460 --> 00:33:14,860
Through the chaos in late Tang dynasty
and Five Dynasties,

711
00:33:15,060 --> 00:33:16,140
people lived a hard life.

712
00:33:16,500 --> 00:33:18,100
Ancestors knew

713
00:33:18,620 --> 00:33:20,740
stability was what people needed the most.

714
00:33:21,380 --> 00:33:24,180
They then made up rules of harmony,

715
00:33:24,580 --> 00:33:26,060
preventing generals from undermining politics,

716
00:33:26,340 --> 00:33:27,820
restraining officials from taking power

717
00:33:27,820 --> 00:33:29,180
and stop relatives from interfering with politics.

718
00:33:29,180 --> 00:33:32,180
They also encouraged remonstration,

719
00:33:32,820 --> 00:33:35,060
to supervise on the emperors.

720
00:33:35,180 --> 00:33:38,060
Chaos prevention is in the first place.

721
00:33:38,060 --> 00:33:39,060
Just like those officials

722
00:33:40,060 --> 00:33:41,500
who are against the reform,

723
00:33:41,500 --> 00:33:43,100
Prime Minister Lv also confuses

724
00:33:43,100 --> 00:33:45,460
the chaos prevention and the fear of mistakes.

725
00:33:45,900 --> 00:33:48,860
They use the latter to cover up their inertia.

726
00:33:48,860 --> 00:33:50,220
But I think

727
00:33:50,220 --> 00:33:51,180
forging ahead

728
00:33:51,300 --> 00:33:53,100
is the real way for chaos prevention.

729
00:33:53,500 --> 00:33:54,540
If we seek peace in fear of mistakes,

730
00:33:55,580 --> 00:33:57,660
new disasters will be bred.

731
00:34:06,620 --> 00:34:07,820
In one hour,

732
00:34:07,820 --> 00:34:08,980
the palace gate will be closed.

733
00:34:09,260 --> 00:34:10,460
I have to go.

734
00:34:11,660 --> 00:34:13,980
Mr. Yan, you can stay for a bit longer.

735
00:34:18,780 --> 00:34:19,780
I will think carefully about

736
00:34:20,780 --> 00:34:25,060
what Fan just said.

737
00:34:43,300 --> 00:34:45,980
Local officials, posterity of meritorious officials

738
00:34:46,900 --> 00:34:49,580
and even imperial clansmen
are cursing Fan Zhongyan.

739
00:34:51,260 --> 00:34:52,380
In only six months,

740
00:34:53,540 --> 00:34:54,900
he’s no longer

741
00:34:54,900 --> 00:34:56,100
a real man

742
00:34:56,100 --> 00:34:57,460
who is honest and pure,

743
00:34:58,260 --> 00:34:59,780
but a ruthless official

744
00:34:59,780 --> 00:35:00,860
who is harsh, mean

745
00:35:01,740 --> 00:35:03,100
and merciless

746
00:35:04,020 --> 00:35:06,020
for his own reputation.

747
00:35:08,540 --> 00:35:09,820
People used to praise him

748
00:35:10,580 --> 00:35:12,380
for being honest and frank.

749
00:35:13,140 --> 00:35:14,820
Now they think he’s hypocritical.

750
00:35:17,060 --> 00:35:18,140
Bao Zheng submitted a report,

751
00:35:18,460 --> 00:35:20,420
complaining that

752
00:35:20,780 --> 00:35:21,700
they had to deal with many trivial affairs

753
00:35:21,860 --> 00:35:24,100
just because of investigation.

754
00:35:25,020 --> 00:35:26,500
And because of impeachment,

755
00:35:27,620 --> 00:35:29,380
Court of Judicial Review

756
00:35:29,380 --> 00:35:30,620
has doubled cases than last year.

757
00:35:31,340 --> 00:35:32,340
However, no officials

758
00:35:32,340 --> 00:35:34,060
have made serious accusations.

759
00:35:34,620 --> 00:35:35,860
Some are trifles,

760
00:35:35,860 --> 00:35:37,260
and even groundless speculations.

761
00:35:38,860 --> 00:35:40,980
He said the reform to dismiss officials

762
00:35:41,780 --> 00:35:43,540
was only in the name of rectification,

763
00:35:44,580 --> 00:35:46,820
which would make all officials worry.

764
00:35:47,460 --> 00:35:48,860
Principles are ignored, instead.

765
00:35:52,220 --> 00:35:53,540
Officer Ren asked me

766
00:35:53,540 --> 00:35:55,260
to check on the performance of officials.

767
00:35:55,460 --> 00:35:56,580
I did for three provinces.

768
00:35:57,180 --> 00:35:58,180
Investigations on officials

769
00:35:58,180 --> 00:35:59,740
have certainly generated

770
00:35:59,740 --> 00:36:00,700
many trifles.

771
00:36:02,340 --> 00:36:04,860
Sometimes, the evidence isn’t conclusive.

772
00:36:05,180 --> 00:36:07,020
A few are only in form.

773
00:36:07,180 --> 00:36:09,380
But most performances
are based on true investigation.

774
00:36:10,180 --> 00:36:11,180
I haven’t found

775
00:36:11,180 --> 00:36:12,900
any investigators who crack down dissidents

776
00:36:13,100 --> 00:36:15,540
blackmail them or take bribe from them.

777
00:36:19,100 --> 00:36:20,460
As time goes on,

778
00:36:20,460 --> 00:36:21,300
some will be braver and do that.

779
00:36:23,180 --> 00:36:26,180
We need people to carry out rules.

780
00:36:26,740 --> 00:36:28,420
All people have selfish desires.

781
00:36:34,660 --> 00:36:36,460
How to eliminate corruption?

782
00:36:38,660 --> 00:36:39,980
Can it be eliminated?

783
00:36:43,700 --> 00:36:45,780
That’s the truth.

784
00:36:46,620 --> 00:36:48,060
But not everything goes

785
00:36:48,060 --> 00:36:49,740
according to truth.

786
00:36:50,860 --> 00:36:52,380
You leave no room

787
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:54,420
when dismissing redundant officials.

788
00:36:56,660 --> 00:36:59,460
You’ve aroused

789
00:36:59,860 --> 00:37:00,940
more and more indignation among people,

790
00:37:02,260 --> 00:37:04,540
including incompetent officials,

791
00:37:04,860 --> 00:37:06,020
old conservative officials,

792
00:37:06,740 --> 00:37:08,620
follower of Prime Minister Lv

793
00:37:08,620 --> 00:37:09,780
who have grudge with you,

794
00:37:09,940 --> 00:37:11,100
those powerful officials

795
00:37:11,100 --> 00:37:13,340
who still want corruption;

796
00:37:14,300 --> 00:37:17,500
or capable officials.

797
00:37:18,460 --> 00:37:20,780
As for the case of Teng Zongliang’s corruption,

798
00:37:22,540 --> 00:37:24,220
Zheng Jian reported him first.

799
00:37:24,420 --> 00:37:26,020
Then Liang Jian impeached him.

800
00:37:26,300 --> 00:37:28,500
Are they incompetent or corrupt?

801
00:37:30,300 --> 00:37:32,620
They are sort of incorruptible
and capable officials.

802
00:37:33,100 --> 00:37:35,100
But they insist that

803
00:37:35,100 --> 00:37:36,460
Teng Zongliang used government funds improperly

804
00:37:37,660 --> 00:37:40,300
and they exaggerated the amount.

805
00:37:41,180 --> 00:37:42,780
Is Teng Zongliang a real avaricious official,

806
00:37:43,460 --> 00:37:45,340
or is he an enemy to them?

807
00:37:47,700 --> 00:37:49,900
So, you also think

808
00:37:49,900 --> 00:37:51,060
they have an ulterior motive

809
00:37:51,060 --> 00:37:52,020
instead of punishing Teng Zongliang?

810
00:37:52,740 --> 00:37:53,420
Good!

811
00:37:53,860 --> 00:37:55,660
Please defend Teng Zijing with me

812
00:37:55,660 --> 00:37:58,340
in front of His Majesty.

813
00:38:03,060 --> 00:38:04,820
You’re already a minister.

814
00:38:05,860 --> 00:38:07,140
I’m sure you’re reasonable.

815
00:38:07,740 --> 00:38:10,860
There is right and wrong in this world.

816
00:38:10,900 --> 00:38:13,220
But people care more for gain and loss.

817
00:38:15,580 --> 00:38:17,100
I work as a minister,

818
00:38:17,900 --> 00:38:19,820
so I want to

819
00:38:20,660 --> 00:38:22,620
make most people in the imperial court

820
00:38:22,620 --> 00:38:24,620
tell right from wrong.

821
00:38:25,300 --> 00:38:26,580
If a minister

822
00:38:26,620 --> 00:38:28,140
must care for gain and loss,

823
00:38:28,140 --> 00:38:29,780
instead of right and wrong,

824
00:38:30,580 --> 00:38:32,860
I’d rather not take power.

825
00:38:34,500 --> 00:38:35,940
As a humble official,

826
00:38:35,940 --> 00:38:38,060
I can even tell right from wrong.

827
00:38:38,300 --> 00:38:39,260
I might be weak,

828
00:38:40,100 --> 00:38:41,820
but it’s better than valuing benefits

829
00:38:41,820 --> 00:38:43,980
with the real power.

830
00:38:44,180 --> 00:38:45,420
Gain and loss

831
00:38:45,500 --> 00:38:48,620
don’t concern you alone.

832
00:38:49,180 --> 00:38:50,140
You’re the minister.

833
00:38:50,260 --> 00:38:52,940
What you think guides others.

834
00:38:53,700 --> 00:38:54,820
What you do

835
00:38:55,300 --> 00:38:57,700
concerns the success of the reform.

836
00:39:00,700 --> 00:39:03,580
If I’ve said or done anything improperly,

837
00:39:03,860 --> 00:39:05,420
feel free to criticize me.

838
00:39:07,980 --> 00:39:10,620
When dismissing redundant officials,

839
00:39:11,580 --> 00:39:14,220
you’ve been fair and merciless.

840
00:39:14,860 --> 00:39:16,260
No one can argue back.

841
00:39:17,100 --> 00:39:18,940
But now, you pledge for Teng Zongliang

842
00:39:19,060 --> 00:39:20,660
without any evidence.

843
00:39:21,620 --> 00:39:22,700
What will people think,

844
00:39:23,980 --> 00:39:25,420
you’re frank

845
00:39:25,980 --> 00:39:28,020
or you attack your enemies

846
00:39:28,180 --> 00:39:29,420
in the name of reform?

847
00:39:31,260 --> 00:39:32,700
I dismiss redundant officials

848
00:39:33,020 --> 00:39:35,140
based on their real performance.

849
00:39:35,660 --> 00:39:38,140
If I misjudge someone for the false performance,

850
00:39:38,140 --> 00:39:38,900
he can reject me

851
00:39:38,900 --> 00:39:40,580
with the real evidence.

852
00:39:41,900 --> 00:39:43,260
I defend Teng Zongliang

853
00:39:43,540 --> 00:39:44,740
because when he used government fund “improperly”,

854
00:39:44,740 --> 00:39:46,260
he governed Jingzhou

855
00:39:46,260 --> 00:39:48,060
and I governed Qing County.

856
00:39:48,420 --> 00:39:50,060
I certainly know

857
00:39:50,180 --> 00:39:51,340
where he used the funds.

858
00:39:51,860 --> 00:39:53,740
You knew and you’re sure.

859
00:39:54,140 --> 00:39:55,820
But do others know?

860
00:39:55,820 --> 00:39:57,260
Is His Majesty sure?

861
00:39:57,860 --> 00:40:00,780
His superior reported him
and the Censor confirmed it.

862
00:40:01,660 --> 00:40:03,500
People may believe or suspect him.

863
00:40:03,660 --> 00:40:05,580
If you vouch for him...

864
00:40:06,100 --> 00:40:08,020
You’re not an ordinary official.

865
00:40:08,020 --> 00:40:08,980
Fan Xiwen.

866
00:40:09,580 --> 00:40:11,220
You’re a minister

867
00:40:11,220 --> 00:40:13,100
who demote and promote many officials.

868
00:40:14,260 --> 00:40:15,700
In people’s eyes,

869
00:40:15,860 --> 00:40:17,460
what you’re doing

870
00:40:18,180 --> 00:40:19,420
makes them worry

871
00:40:19,620 --> 00:40:21,020
if you’re defending your friends

872
00:40:21,340 --> 00:40:24,300
and cracking down dissidents

873
00:40:24,300 --> 00:40:25,620
in the name of the reform.

874
00:40:26,780 --> 00:40:28,460
In people’s eyes?

875
00:40:30,540 --> 00:40:32,740
Which matters more,

876
00:40:32,940 --> 00:40:34,260
people’s eyes or the truth?

877
00:40:35,300 --> 00:40:36,580
Where is the truth?

878
00:40:37,700 --> 00:40:38,740
In your heart?

879
00:40:39,860 --> 00:40:41,380
Who can see through your heart?

880
00:40:41,980 --> 00:40:45,140
People all think differently.

881
00:40:46,780 --> 00:40:48,020
You’re a high-ranking official,

882
00:40:48,380 --> 00:40:50,580
concerning the safety and interests of many people.

883
00:40:51,460 --> 00:40:53,020
Except the frankness in your heart,

884
00:40:53,460 --> 00:40:55,220
you should also put on a show

885
00:40:55,820 --> 00:40:57,900
to relieve people.

886
00:41:18,420 --> 00:41:19,380
I can’t do that!

887
00:41:21,860 --> 00:41:22,740
What?

888
00:41:25,660 --> 00:41:26,300
I can’t

889
00:41:26,300 --> 00:41:27,940
hide the truth,

890
00:41:28,300 --> 00:41:29,940
just to show the so-called fairness.

891
00:41:32,900 --> 00:41:34,500
When Ge Huaimin suffered a defeat,

892
00:41:34,500 --> 00:41:36,220
the border was in danger and people were worried.

893
00:41:36,500 --> 00:41:38,140
Teng Zongliang made a prompt decision

894
00:41:38,220 --> 00:41:39,420
and rushed out for border business.

895
00:41:39,420 --> 00:41:41,060
He collected people, awarded generals,

896
00:41:41,540 --> 00:41:43,380
treated Qiang leaders nicely

897
00:41:43,620 --> 00:41:45,300
and asked neighboring troops for help.

898
00:41:45,700 --> 00:41:47,420
I certainly know

899
00:41:47,580 --> 00:41:49,020
where he used the government funds.

900
00:41:49,780 --> 00:41:51,780
If I don’t tell the truth,

901
00:41:51,780 --> 00:41:53,940
and let someone bring a false charge

902
00:41:53,940 --> 00:41:55,300
against his selfish interests,

903
00:41:55,300 --> 00:41:56,460
confuse right and wrong

904
00:41:56,460 --> 00:41:57,980
and turn a meritorious official into a guilty one,

905
00:41:58,180 --> 00:41:59,340
I’ll be cheating His Majesty.

906
00:42:02,260 --> 00:42:04,140
I will try my best

907
00:42:04,140 --> 00:42:05,340
to find the witness and evidence.

908
00:42:06,460 --> 00:42:07,580
Even if I fail,

909
00:42:08,260 --> 00:42:10,540
I’ll tell His Majesty whatever I know.

910
00:42:13,260 --> 00:42:15,020
Only His Majesty decides

911
00:42:15,300 --> 00:42:16,980
if I’m a qualified minister.

912
00:42:18,140 --> 00:42:19,620
If His Majesty thinks

913
00:42:20,460 --> 00:42:22,700
what I’m doing

914
00:42:23,100 --> 00:42:25,060
does no good to

915
00:42:25,460 --> 00:42:26,540
our nation, people or the Emperor,

916
00:42:27,580 --> 00:42:32,740
he can relegate me, banish me or kill me.

917
00:42:33,980 --> 00:42:35,180
But when I work as a minister,

918
00:42:35,860 --> 00:42:37,420
I think of nothing,

919
00:42:38,340 --> 00:42:39,340
except fairness and truth.

